(333, 'E2-0333AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, March 6) 1st indorsement', 'Respectfully forwarded to UP Diliman Chancellor Dr. Jose V. Abueva, through Budget Director Prof. Honesto G. Nuqui, recommending approval of the herein request to purchase additional computing hardware and software and to allocate from the UPD equipment outlay the sum of P368,000 for the said purchase.\nThe acquisition of such a system would significantly enhance our Computer Science and Computer Engineering Programs by providing our students with additional experience with a multi-user system as well as the use of Computer Aided Design Software. ', 'Garcia, Dr. Ruben A.\nAbueva, Dr. Jose V. \nNuqui, Prof. Honesto G. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(334, 'E2-0334AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, July 4) UP Diliman S&T Park ', 'In response to your request dated 25 April 1990 for support of the pilot project to establish the UP Diliman S&T Park, please be informed that after extensive discussions in the DOST, we believe that your proposal should be integrated into a general plan to establish such a park in the UP Diliman campus. Units such as the College of Science, College of Business Administration and UPISSI have expressed interest in such an activity in informal talks with DOST officials. ', 'Garcia, Dr. Ruben \nGopez, Adolfo Jesus R. \nPhilippine Council for Industry & Energy Research & Development ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
