(372, 'E2-0372AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1988, September 19)  List of Faculty who are expected to complete their Ph.D.\'s', 'In response to your memorandum dated 8 August 1988 requesting for a list of faculty members who are expecting to complete their PhD\'s (re : Memorandum 23 dated 6 November 1985), we are submitting the following information:\n1. Edwin Quiros, expecting his PhD in April 1989\n2. Ferdinand Manegdeg, PhD in November 1989\n3. Amante Mangaser, PhD in December 1989\n4. Joselito Sarreal, PhD in late 1989', 'Garcia, Dr. Ruben A. \nTabujara, Dr. Ernesto G. \nPacheco, Dr. Edgardo S. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
