(377, 'E2-0377AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1989, April 26) Request for assistance from CESELEC to develop university courses in Electrical Eng', 'The College of Engineering of the University of the Philippines at Diliman (U.P.) would like to request the assistance of French experts through CESELEC for a program of academic cooperation with the Department of Electrical Engineering for the purpose of improving teaching capability in selected areas of Electrical Engineering which are described in the attached proposal. ', 'Pierron, Georges\nGarcia, Dr. Ruben A. \nCentre d\'Etudes Superieures en Electricite, Electronique et Informatique (CESELEC)', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
