(387, 'E2-0387AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, April 30) Proposal for Financial Assistance for R&D Projects/Programs ', 'We are pleased to inform you that PNSS has approved a follow-up study for the design and development of the organizational and operating details of the technology park to be set up in UP Diliman Campus. This study includes the putting up of several pilot projects utilizing available facilities at the College of Engineering  ', 'Gopez, Dr. Adolfo Jesus R.\nGarcia, Dr. Ruben A. \nTechnology Park ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
