(390, 'E2-0390AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1985, July 8) Designation as members of a Sub-Committee to Assist the University Committee on Bids ', 'You are hereby designated as a Sub-Committee to assist the University on Bids and Awards (Supplies, Materials and Equipment) in the purchase by bidding of IBN compatible microcomputers for B.S. Computer Science Program. Dr. Honesto G. Nuqui and Prof. Jose Ma. de Castro shall serve as resource persons. ', 'Tabujara, Ernesto G. \nVea, Prof. Reynaldo B.\nFrancisco, Prof. Leonardo D.\nAtanacio, Prof. Edgar L.', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(391, 'E2-0391AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1985, August 14) Memorandum for : The Executive Committee, College of Engineering', 'Please be informed that the Executive Committee will have a meeting at 2:00 PM on Wednesday, August 21, 1985 at MH 208. ', 'Gopez, Adolfo Jesus R.', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(392, 'E2-0392AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1985, August 26) Memorandum for : Department Chairmen ', 'In preparation for the faculty meeting scheduled on Wednesday, 28 August 1985 at 1:00 PM., MH 410, please find attached material on the General Education Program which is on file with the Administrative Program of the College, and material on the proposed National Telecommunications Institute. \nPlease be informed that the title of the Aber P. Canlas Chair is : Aber P. Canlas Professorial Chair in Project Construction Management, specific field : Project Implementation. This is a UP Foundation Inc. - chair. No particular requirements are demanded of the chair-holder other than those already being applied by the Foundation. Please prepare the name (s) of your nominee (s) for the next Executive Committee meeting. ', 'Gopez, Adolfo Jesus R.', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(393, 'E2-0393AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1985, August 29) Memorandum for : Executive Committee ', 'Please be informed that the Executive Committee will hold a special meeting on Tuesday, 3 September 1985, 11:30 AM to 12 NN at MH 208, to review the college viewpoint on the General Education Program which will be presented at the system wide workshop on September 4 and 5. ', 'Garcia, Dr. Ruben A. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(394, 'E2-0394AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1985, September 17) Memorandum No. 11 : Three-Day College Teaching Workshop', 'With reference to our memorandum dated September 6, 1985, we are sending herewith information details about the 3-day College Teaching Seminar-Workshop to be conducted by the College of Education on October 15-17, 1985.\nThis is the first of three 3-day modules with different emphases.\nThe three modules are : \nA. Preparation for Teaching at the University Level : An Overview for the Teaching Scholar (October 15-17, 1985)\nB. College Teaching : Methods, Techniques and Strategies (Tentatively scheduled late November, 1985)\nC. Evaluation of Instruction at the College Level (Tentatively scheduled 2nd week of December, 1985) ', 'Ramos, Paz G. \n', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(395, 'E2-0395AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1986, April 22) Memorandum No. 12 : Ten-Day College Teaching Workshop\nSeminar-Workshop on College T', 'A 10-day seminar workshop on College Teaching will be conducted by the College of Education for new instructors as well as for experienced faculty members who may wish to update themselves on teaching and teaching methods. The seminar-workshop will be held on May 20-30, 1986. ', 'Ramos, Paz G. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
