(410, 'E2-0410AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'CSC Memorandum Circular No. 9 s. 1989 Revised Guidelines in the Conduct of Government Training and D', 'In line with the present thrust of government towards decentralization and deregulation, coupled with its drive towards cost effectiveness in government operations, the following guidelines in the administration of agency training and development progams shall be observed. ', 'Government Training and Development Programs \nSto. Tomas, Patricia A. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
