(414, 'E2-0414AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, February 16) Memorandum No. 08 : Reiteration of procedure in proposing new academic programs ', 'As a reminder to all concerned, this Office reissues Memorandum No. 51 of 31 August 1988, copy attached. Kindly help us and the Board of Regents plan academic policy in a most rational way by observing the steps outlined in the memorandum. ', 'Abueva, Jose V. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(415, 'E2-0415AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1998, August 31) Memorandum No. 51 : Prior notice about new academic programs before actual process', 'Please inform us, through the Chancellor, about any new academic program you may wish to propose for final approval by the Board of Regents. That is : inform us about the concept before it is actually submitted to the appropriate academic bodies, from the Departmental level to the University Council. By concept is meant a brief working proposal : what the new program is, why it should be established, and possible budgetary requirements. By new academic program is meant a new curricular program or course of study (not individual subjects nor revisions of already existing programs); or a new certificate, post-baccalaureate, or non-degree course of study. ', 'Abueva, Jose V. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(416, 'E2-0416AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, February 28) Memorandum No. 04 : U.P. Review and Planning Workshop on Science and Technology ', 'Areas to be addressed by a constituent University\'s Science and Technology Plan\nI. Programs (Graduate, Undergraduate, Research and Extension Programs)\nII. Faculty and Staff Development Plan\nIII. Physical Plan (Buildings, Facilities, Laboratories and Equipment)\nIV. Linkages\nV. Financial Requirements and Possible Sources of Funds/Resources ', 'Abueva, Jose V. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(417, 'E2-0417AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, May 26) U.P. Review and Planning Workshop on Science and Technology : April 3-4, 1990, U.P. D', 'The Program of Activities for the Workshop (copy attached) was finalized after meeting with the Steering Committee and the Commitee Chairpersons. Please circulate copies of the program to your faculty who will participate in the Workshop. ', 'Abueva, Jose V. \nAbad, Gemino H. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(418, 'E2-0418AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, June 26) Memorandum for The Executive Committee, Division of Engineering and Industrial Resea', 'By direction of Dr. Achilles del Callar, Chairman, Division of Engineering and Industrial Research, please be informed that there will be an Executive Committee meeting on Monday, 16 July 1990 at 8:30 in the morning at the UPAA Hostel, Magsaysay Ave., Diliman, Quezon City.\nAgenda : \n1. Engineering Encyclopedia\n2. Evaluation of Science and Technology Park\n3. Other matters ', 'Ona, Edna O.', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(419, 'E2-0419AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1990, August 8) Memorandum No. 90-01 for Deans, College Secretaries, Department Chairmen, and Membe', 'The Committee on Curriculum discussed at its meeting on 29 June 1990 the problems of students from regional units who have finished courses and/or programs in regional units and who later seek transfer to a unit on the Diliman campus. ', 'Garcia, Ester A.', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
