(425, 'E2-0425AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1971, September) Annual report to Ford Foundation on University of the Philippines, College of Engi', 'This report will cover the programmatic activities for the University of the Philippines College of Engineering from the period July 1, 1970 through June 30, 1971, reviewing the status of the project by grant category generally, commenting on performance, and, where deemed appropriate, provide recommendations relative to future activity. ', 'Warner, J.C.\nNowak, Frank E. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
