(437, 'E2-0437AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1979, August 13) Notification of Appointment ', 'The following are hereby appointed as members of the College Committee on Student Organizations, Activities, and Welfare, for the academic year 1979-1980:\nDr. Danilo Mangaoang, Chairman\nMr. Alfonso Aguilar, Jr. Member\nMr. Edgardo Mayor, Member\nMr. Eugene Gonzales, Member \nIt shall be the duty of the Committee to consider policies covering student organizations, activities and welfare, and suggest to the Dean, thru the College Officer for Student Relations, proposals affecting the above-mentioned matters. ', 'Mena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(438, 'E2-0438AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1979, September 24) Notification of Appointment ', 'The following are hereby appointed to the College Committee on Private Scholarships in Engineering effective October 1, 1979 : \nMs. Rosalinda R. Arenas, Chairman\nProf. Rodolfo M. Casiple, Member\nMs. Armi V. Exmundo, Member \nThe Committee shall be in charge of selecting grantees as well as policies and problems affecting private scholarships in engineering ', 'Mena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(439, 'E2-0439AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1980, July 30) Notification of Appointments', 'The following are hereby reappointed to the College Committee on Admissions and Readmissions effective July 1, 1980 until June 30, 1982 : \nProf. Rodolfo U. Bulatao, Chairman\nMr. Miguel T. Escoto, Jr., Member\nMrs. Maria Luz S. Vencio, Member \nThe Committee shall be in charge of admission of new students as well as readmission of dismissed students in the College of Engineering ', 'Mena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(440, 'E2-0440AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1980, August 20) Notification of Appointment', 'The following are hereby appointed as members of the College Committees on Student Organizations, Activities and Welfare, for the academic year 1980-1981 : \nAlfonso L. Aguilar, Jr., Chairman\nEduardo S. Mayor, Member\nAlexander Paran, Member\nMacario Pavia, Member\nESC Chairman, Member \nIt shall be the duty of the Committee to consider policies covering student organizations, activities and welfare, and suggest to the Dean proposals affecting the above-mentioned matters. ', 'Mena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(441, 'E2-0441AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1981, January 13) Notification of Appointment ', 'The following are hereby appointed to the College Committee on Private Scholarships in Engineering effective 1 February 1981 : \nDr. Teresita F. Bala, Chairman\nProf. Rodolfo M. Casiple, Member\nMr. Benito Pacheco, Member\nThe Committee shall be in charge of selecting grantees as well as in formulating policies and guidelines affecting private scholarships in engineering.', 'Mena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
