(448, 'E2-0448AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1983, April 19) Office Order No. 03-83 College Energy Committee', 'You are hereby appointed as members of the College Energy Committee with Dr. Ruben A. Garcia as Chairman. ', 'Garcia, Dr. Ruben A.\nViray, Dr. Francisco L.\nFestin, Teodorico F.\nLiongson, Leonardo Q.\nDela Cruz, Armando \nMena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(449, 'E2-0449AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1983, June 24) Office Order No. 04-83 : College Research Committee ', 'As agreed upon during the meeting of the College Executive Committee last June 22, 1983, you are hereby constituted as the College Research Committee for academic year 1983-1984. The Committee will perform the following functions : \n1. Screen and recommend proposals for UPERDFI-funded research;\n2. Screen and recommend publications that will be eligible for the UPERDFI cash awards;\n3. Screen and recommend graduate fellows who will be eligible for UPERDFI financial support. ', 'Viray, Francisco L.\nGuererro, Perfecto K.\nPacheco, Edgardo S.\nHernandez, Manuel V. Jr.\nDela Cruz, Armando A. \nMena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(450, 'E2-0450AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1983, August 1) : Miguel B. Escoto, Officer in Charge ', 'By virtue of Executive Order No. 19, dated December 5, 1969, you are hereby designated Office-In-Charge of the College of Engineering effective August 2, 1983 until the return of the undersigned on August 5, 1983. ', 'Mena, Marino M. \nEscoto, Miguel B. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(451, 'E2-0451AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1983, August 26) Office Order No. 06-83 : Armando A. Dela Cruz, Officer in Charge ', 'By virtue of Executive Order No. 19, dated December 5, 1969, you are hereby designated Officer-In-Charge of the Department of Industrial Engineering effective August 27 until September 3, 1983 when Prof. Fortunato T. dela Peña shall have returned from his trip to Australia. ', 'Mena, Marino M. \nDela Cruz, Armando A. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(452, 'E2-0452AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1984, March 26) Office Order No. 01-84 : Dr. Manuel V. Hernandez, Jr. , Officer in Charge', 'By virtue of Executive Order No. 19, dated December 5, 1969, you are hereby designated Officer-In-Charge of the Department of Industrial Engineering effective March 26 until April 1, 1984 when Prof. Fortunato T. dela Peña shall have returned from his trip to Australia. ', 'Mena, Marino M. \nHernandez, Dr. Manuel V. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(453, 'E2-0453AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1984, April 24) Office Order No. 02-84 : Appointment to the College Committee on Admissions and Rea', 'You are hereby appointed to compose the College Committee on Admissions and Readmissions with Dr. Mena as Chairman, effective June 1, 1984.\nThe Committee is in charge of admission of new students as well as the readmission of dismissed students in the College of Engineering. ', 'Mena, Marino M.\nMena, Manolo G.\nParan, Alexander P.\nVencio, Ma. Luz S. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(454, 'E2-0454AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1984, June 29) Office Order No. 04-84 : College Research and Publications Committee', 'Please be informed that the College Executive Committee during its meeting last June 27, 1984 had designated you as members of the College Research and Publications Committee with Dr. Rogelio A. Panlasigui as Chairman effective July 1, 1984. ', 'Panlasigui, Rogelio A.\nAbaya, Efren F.\nJesus, Adolfo\nHernandez, Manuel V. Jr. \nRañeses, Nestor O. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(455, 'E2-0455AC', '', '', '', '', '', 'Preamble\nArticle I - Name\nArticle II - Powers & Duties\nArticle III - Composition\nArticle IV - The Council Officers and Members \nArticle V - Committees\nArticle VI - Elections\nArticle VII - Meetings\nArticle VIII - The Council Adviser\nArticle IX - Impeachment of Officers, Suspension and Expulsion of Members \nArticle X - Finances of the Council\nArticle XI - Publication of the College Student Paper\nArticle XII - Provisions for Amendments\nArticle XIII - Effectivity\nArticle XIV - Transitory Provisions ', '', 'Proposed Constitution of the University of the Philippines Eng\'g Student Council ', 'Preamble\nWe, the students of the U.P. College of Engineering, in order to establish a relevant Student Council that shall promote student welfare and advance student rights, develop, direct, and channel our Engineering skills, knowledge, and talents towards nation-building, and commit ourselves to the interests of the Filipino people, do hereby ordain and promulgate this Constitution. ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
