(466, 'E2-0466AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1980, April 11-12) Program : 1980 UP Engineering Conference \nEducation of Engineers : Current Trend', 'The conference is intended to provide a forum for discussing relevant issues related to the characteristics and demands of the engineer\'s profession today as well as ways and means of incorporating new dimensions in engineering education and training ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
