(469, 'E2-0469AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1981, March 3) Invitation to the Athletic Commencement', 'The Institute of Sports, Physical Education and Recreation cordially invites you to the Athletic Commencement which will be held in the U.P. Gym on Sunday, 8 March 1981. The general program includes a swimming competition among all the varsity athletes (except the swimmers of course) in the morning at 8:00 to 11:00.', 'Abad Santos, Cynthia V.\nMena, Marino M. ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(470, 'E2-0470AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1981, September 18) Invitation to a seminar-lecture on \"What is Cartography?\"', 'The Philippine Society of Photogrammetry and The Training Center for Applied Geodesy and Photogrammetry cordially invite you to a Seminar-Lecture at the GE Seminar Room, 4th Floor, UP College of Engineering Diliman, Quezon City at 2:00 p.m. on September 18, 1981 on the subject What is Cartography? to be given by Mr. Byrne Goodrich, Consultant', 'Mena, Marino M. \nGoodrich, Byrne ', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
