(1373, 'E2-1373AC', '', 'Memorandum from the Chairman ', 'Republic of the Philippines\nOffice of the President ', 'Commission on Higher Education', 'March 16, 2004', 'Message of her Excellency President Gloria Macapagal - Arroyo for the Graduating Students ', '', '', 'In accordance with the mandate of Republic Act (RA) 7722, otherwise known as \"Higher Education Act of 1994, and in line with Administrative Order No. 95 dated February 27, 2004, you are hereby informed that: 1. Her Excellency President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo has issued a message for graduating students that is requested to be read by the designated cabinet secretary or the Head of the Higher Education Institution during the graduation ceremony. 2. The designated Cabinet Officers for Regional Development (CORD) shall be with Her Excellency\'s representative during the graduation ceremony. ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
