(1405, 'E2-1405AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1998, November 16) The Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi', 'Dear Prof. Atanacio, \nGreetings!\nThe Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi cordially invites you to its Alumni Homecoming and Christmas Party on 3 December 1998 from 3:30 -^;30 P.M. to be held at the College of Home Economics Tearoom U.P. Diliman Campus. \nWe are looking forward to seeing you and joining us in our fellowship.\nVery truly yours,\n\nSONIA Y. DE LEON\nPresident ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(1406, 'E2-1406AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1998, January 28) The Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi', 'Dean Edgardo G. Atanacio\nCollege of Engineering\nUniversity of the Philippines\nDiliman, Quezon City\n\nDear Dean Atanacio, \nI am pleased to invite you to the 16th Scholars Recognition Convocation on Wednesday, February 4, 1998 from 3:00 - 5:00 p.m., at Malcolm Hall, College of Law, U.P. Diliman, Quezon City. On this occasion, 83 outstanding seniors of the University of the Philippines for AY 1997-1998 chosen by the International Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi, Pi Gamma Mu and the Phi Sigma Biological Honor Society will be honored. Dr. Reynaldo Vea, the former dean of the College of Engineering and MWSS Administrator will give the inspirational message. \nA reception will follow the convocation. If you are attending please call Marci or Dhang at the University Center for Women\'s Studies, telephone # 920-53-01 loc. 4933 and 920-6880.\nPlease join us in celebrating scholarly achivement and academic excellence. \nSincerely, \n\nSylvia H. Guerrero, Ph.D.\nPresident ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(1407, 'E2-1407AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1998, January 28) The Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi', 'To : All members of the Honor Society of Phi Kappa Phi, U.P. Chapter\nFrom : Dr. Sylvia H. Guerrero\nPresident\nGreetings for the New Year!\nI am happy to announce the selection of 28 students as Phi Kappa Phi outstanding seniors this AY 1997-1998. Together with the awardees of Phi Sigma and Pi Gamma Mu, they will be honored during the 16th Scholars Recognition Convocation, to be held on Wednesday, February 4, 1998 at 3:00 P.M., Malcolm Hall, College of Law, U.P. Diliman, Quezon City.\nPlease join us as we honor them in this special convocation.\nCall Marci/Dhang at U.P. Center for Women\'s Studies Tel. No. 920-6880 to confirm your attendance. ', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
