(1421, 'E2-1421AC', '', 'The U.P. College of Music & the Office for Initiatives in Culture & the Arts present DAWANI II a concert featuring the U.P. Madrigal Singers', '', '', 'February 1, 2001\n6:00 P.M.\nAbelardo Hall Auditorium', '', 'Invitation', '(2001, January 29)', 'University of the Philippines\nCollege of Music\nDiliman, Quezon City\n\nProf. Edgardo J. Atanacio\nDean\nCollege of Engineering\nU.P. Diliman, Quezon City\n\nDear Dean Atanacio :\n\nWith Dawani II, the College of Music will usher in all the Abelardo Hall concerts scheduled for February, declared, National Arts Month and UP Diliman Month. The famed UP Madrigal singers, led by National Artist Andrea O. Veneracion, will perform a rich repertoire of madrigals, spirituals, international folksongs, and their own original arrangements of popular songs like On My Own, Anak and Circle of Life\n\nPlease honor us with your presence on Thursday, February 1, 2001, 6:00 p.m. at Abelardo Hall.\n\nSincerely yours, \n\nGEMMA FILIPINA T. MALICDEM\nCollege Secretary', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
