(1451, 'E2-1451AC', '', 'Pagpapahalaga', '', '', 'July 20, 1999\nBahay ng Alumni\nUP Diliman, Quezon City', '', '', '', 'The Chancellor of UP Diliman\nDr. Claro T. Llaguno\ninvites you to \nPAGPAPAHALAGA\n\nA Tribute to President Emil Q. Javier\non 20 July 1999\nat the Bahay ng Alumni\nUP Diliman, Quezon City\n\ncocktails at 6 pm\nwith the Athenaeum String Quartet\n\nconcert at 7 pm\nwith the UP Concert Chorus\n\ndinner and program at 7:30 pm\n\ndance at 8:30 pm\nwith the UP Jazz Ensemble', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
