(1557, 'E2-1557AC', '', 'The Sixth Alejandro Melchor Memorial Lecture ', '', '', '', 'The Sixth Alejandro Melchor Memorial Lecture to be delivered by Engineer Filemon T. Berba, Jr. Ayala Corporation\n\n3 O\'clock P.M.\nAugust 9, 2001\nEngineering Library \nGround Floor, Melchor Hall\nU.P. Diliman\n\nSponsored by : \nCollege of Engineering, U.P. Diliman\nU.P. Engineering Research and Development Foundation, Inc.\nU.P. Alumni Engineers\nBeta Epsilon Fraternity', 'Invitation', 'PROGRAMME \nPambansang Awit\nOpening Remarks by Prof. D. I. Ilio\nUP Alumni Engineers\n\"The Mind and Hea', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(1558, 'E2-1558AC', '', 'Alejandro Melchor Centennial Book ', 'Diliman, Quezon City ', 'College of Engineering\nUniversity of the Philippines', '2000', 'By Way of An Introduction by Dominador I. Ilio\nAlejandro Melchor\nEngineering \'24, Philippine Army, Distinguished Alumnus of the University of the Philippines, Scientist, and above all a Gentleman and a Soldier. \nThe U.P. Alumni Engineers\nDedication Ceremonies, April 6, 1963\nAlejandro Melchor : A Son\'s Perspective by Alejandro Melchor, Jr. \nProfessor Melchor Remembered by Dominador I. Ilio\nAlejandro Melchor\nMelchor Hall Trivia \nThe Lolo I never met by Soliman M. Santos, Jr. \nDynamo of an Organizer\nWhat they had to say about Alejandro Melchor', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
(1559, 'E2-1559AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1998, January 9) ', 'Republic of the Philippines\nOffice of the President\nCOMMISSION ON HIGHER EDUCATION\nRegion IX, Zamboanga City\n\nJanuary 9, 1998\n\nThe Chairman\nMeralco Award for Engineering and Applied Sciences\nSecretariat, Corporation Communication\nMeralco, Ortigas Avenue\nPasig City\n\nSir, \n\nWe are sending herewith the Nomination Form and other supporting documents of Mr. Carlos A. Abarro and Arch. Domingo A. Abarro III for consideration to the Annual Meralco Award for Engineering and applied Sciences. \n\nVery truly yours, \n\nBernabella LL. Panganiban \nOIC, Chief', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
