(1618, 'E2-1618AC', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '(1986, November 7) Curriculum and Course Revision', 'The Registrar\nUniversity of the Philippines\nDiliman, Quezon City\n\nSubject : Curriculum and Course Revisions\n\nMadam : \n\nThe College of Engineering submits for consideration the following curricular revisions and proposals : \na) Proposed courses in Biotechnology and Biochemical Engineering. \nb) Proposed abolition and institution of courses in Electrical Engineering. \nc) Proposed revisions in the Bachelor of Computer Science Program. \nd) Proposed revisions in the Undergraduate Program in Civil Engineering. \ne) Proposed revisions in the Graduate Program in Civil Engineering. \nf) Renumbering of courses : Environmental Engineering Graduate Program.\ng) Proposed revisions in the Undergraduate and Graduate Programs in Mechanical Engineering. \nh) Proposed revisions in the Undergraduate Program in Geodetic Engineering. \ni) Revisions of Bachelor of Science (Metallurgical Engineering).\n\nNineteen other copies of each of the above-stated proposals have been submitted directly to Cluster C Chairman, Dr. Edgardo S. Pacheco.\n\nVery truly yours,\n\nADOLFO JESUS R. GOPEZ, Dr. - Ing\nCollege Secretary\n\nCopy furnished : Dr. Edgardo S. Pacheco', '', NULL, NULL, 'Public (Metadata Only)', 'active', '2026-03-18 08:36:49', '2026-03-18 08:36:49'),
